A bunch of Capetonians are showing the world how to do selfies right by taking incredible photos of themselves with a drone to capture their locations in various beautiful spots across the Mother City. The video features South African celebs and entertainers like Katlego Maboe and Leigh-Anne Williams, all sharing locations on the broader map that is Cape Town. The video was created for a competition called #BreakTheNet, a digital reality show looking for the next YouTube sensation, hosted by Cell C. 